/--
`max‚ÇÉ j‚ÇÅ j‚ÇÇ j‚ÇÉ` is an arbitrary choice of object to the right of `j‚ÇÅ`, `j‚ÇÇ` and `j‚ÇÉ`,
whose existence is ensured by `is_filtered`.
